    answer: "Workshops range from half-day introductory sessions to multi-day comprehensive programs, depending on your team's needs and current AI literacy level."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you offer AI training in Huntsville?",
    answer: "Yes, we provide on-site AI training throughout North Alabama including Huntsville, Florence, the Shoals area, Decatur, and Athens. Remote training is also available."
